To voices in opposition,

00:41:08.916 --> 00:41:22.496 line:90% position:50% align:center
Those who would make me stray
From the path I’m on today?

00:41:22.496 --> 00:41:29.003 line:90% position:50% align:center
To whom
could I go away?

00:41:29.003 --> 00:41:34.742 line:90% position:50% align:center
Where could I turn
in times of trouble?

00:41:34.742 --> 00:41:40.214 line:90% position:50% align:center
To whom
could I go away?

00:41:40.214 --> 00:41:46.120 line:90% position:50% align:center
