With my place in his care,

00:42:14.882 --> 00:42:20.888 line:90% position:50% align:center
Surrounded by love
In the faith that we share.

00:42:20.888 --> 00:42:26.660 line:90% position:50% align:center
I look to the future
That Jehovah provides.

00:42:26.660 --> 00:42:33.934 line:90% position:50% align:center
His Son is my Savior
With sayings of life.

00:42:35.569 --> 00:42:47.147 line:90% position:50% align:center
I will never listen
To voices in opposition.

00:42:47.147 --> 00:43:00.761 line:90% position:50% align:center
