From the path I’m on today?

00:43:00.761 --> 00:43:07.635 line:90% position:50% align:center
To whom
could I go away?

00:43:07.635 --> 00:43:13.140 line:90% position:50% align:center
Where could I turn
in times of trouble?

00:43:13.140 --> 00:43:18.479 line:90% position:50% align:center
To whom
could I go away?

00:43:18.479 --> 00:43:24.551 line:90% position:50% align:center
The voice of the stranger
Leads only to danger.

00:43:24.551 --> 00:43:33.994 line:90% position:50% align:center
It’s Jesus’ words I hear
and obey.

00:43:35.696 --> 00:43:42.169 line:90% position:50% align:center
To whom
could I go away?

00:43:42.169 --> 00:43:47.808 line:90% position:50% align:center
Where could I turn
in times of trouble?

00:43:47.808 --> 00:43:53.047 line:90% position:50% align:center
To whom
